author: Goethe
message: Just trust yourself, then you will know how to live.
title: Thought of the day

author: Pema Chodron
message: To be fully alive, fully human, and completely awake is to be continually thrown out of the nest.
title: Thought of the day

author: Jim Rohn
message: If you don't design your own life plan, chances are you'll fall into someone else's plan. And guess what they have planned for you? Not much.
title: Thought of the day

author: Carl Jung
message: It all depends on how we look at things, and not how they are in themselves.
title: Thought of the day
